          │  • Scoped to selected district
          ▼
  STEP 7: Login with Email + Password
          │  • Optional MFA (TOTP or SMS OTP)
          ▼
  [District Admin Dashboard Access]


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  2.3  VILLAGE OFFICER MOBILE ONBOARDING FLOW
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  [District Admin Dashboard]
          │
          ▼
  STEP 1: District Admin Enters Officer Credentials
          │  • Employee ID
          │  • NIDA Number
          │  • Email address
          ▼
  STEP 2: NIDA Lookup → auto-fill bio data
          ▼
  STEP 3: Email Dispatch
          │  • Token + mobile app download link sent to officer email
          ▼
  STEP 4: Officer Installs App & Enters Token
          │  • Opens app → enters one-time token
          │
          │  [BACKGROUND PROCESSES — runs silently after token accepted]
          │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────┐
          │  │ a) Capture device fingerprint           │
          │  │    (device ID + OS + hardware hash)     │
          │  │ b) Record GPS coordinates               │
          │  │ c) Bind officer to device (1 device     │
          │  │    only — cannot change without admin)  │
          │  │ d) Store village geo-fence polygon      │
          │  │ e) If all OK → unlock next page         │
          │  └────────────────────────────────────────┘
          ▼
  STEP 5: Profile Setup
          │  • New password + confirm
          │  • Profile photo (take with camera)
          │  • Valid mobile number
          │  • Ward name
          │  • Village name
          │  • Region & District (auto-filled by admin scope)
          ▼
  STEP 6: Account Activated — Geo-Locked
          │  • App validates GPS on EVERY session start
          │  • If officer is outside village boundary → app blocked
          │  • If device ID doesn't match bound device → app blocked
          ▼
  STEP 7: Login with Email + Password
          │  • Optional MFA
          ▼
  [Village Officer App — Full Access within Village Boundary]


